Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.93,0:24:57.16,Default,,0,0,50,,If you are a man, don't lose your heart{男だったら　くじけるな}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.16,0:25:05.61,Default,,0,0,50,,Because there's just you and me, a man and a man{俺もおまえも　男と男}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.61,0:25:13.96,Default,,0,0,50,,With crimson blood flowing in our veins all the same{おなじ真赤な　血が通う}
